1.title: Secrets of a Trophy Wife
1.plot: SECRETS OF A TROPHY WIFE explores the elite lifestyles of trophy wives, and the men they strive to keep happy. Juggling their own businesses and families can be challenging, especially when the next wannabe trophy wife is always waiting in line.

2.title: Cheer Perfection
2.plot: Cheerleading coach Alisha Dunlap expects perfection from the kids in her gym. This pressure is just fine for the competitive moms who admit that they're living through their children. But when two moms feud, one of their little girls pushed to the brink.

3.title: Jersey on Ice
3.plot: In New Jersey, figure skating not only takes grace, dedication, and hard work - it also takes a thick skin. Especially when the no-nonsense coaches, sisters Deana, Andrea and lifelong friend Michele, step on the ice.

4.title: Vegas Brides: Royal Flush
4.plot: Beauty queen and former Mrs. Nevada threatens to cancel her wedding over dress anxiety while another bride might miss her wedding due to indecision.

5.title: Vegas Brides: The Full Monty
5.plot: When the bride is going to be the only one clothed at her wedding the gown better make a statement and a renaissance themed wedding has a bride and groom seeing color.

6.title: Best Funeral Ever
6.plot: The staff at Golden Gate Funeral Home throws outrageously themed funerals. From a BBQ-themed ceremony to a funeral celebrating the Christmas spirit, Golden Gate proves that, while you may be in casket -- it can still be fantastic.

imdb.plot outline: Meet rivaling ice-skating coaches Deana and Andrea in Jersey on Ice and the coaches who will say anything to attend the national finals on Cheer Perfection. Observe ostentatiously fabulous funerals in Best Funeral Ever, watch as the dress searching drama unfolds in Vegas Brides, and see how some women seem to have it all in Secrets of a Trophy Wife.
